<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/brand-assets/logo_reply-ai_thumbnail.svg">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <title>Crea tu cuenta en reply-ai</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl w-full max-w-md border border-gray-100">
                <% if flash[:alert] %>
                    <div class="mb-6 text-center bg-red-50 border border-red-200 text-red-700 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl font-semibold">
                        <%= flash[:alert] %>
                    </div>
                <% elsif flash[:notice] %>
                    <div class="mb-6 text-center bg-green-50 border border-green-200 text-green-700 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl font-semibold">
                        <%= flash[:notice] %>
                    </div>
                <% end %>
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <img src="/brand-assets/logo_reply-ai.png" alt="reply-ai" class="h-12 mx-auto mb-4">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-800">Registrar Cuenta</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">Complete los datos e inicie sesión en su cuenta de MercadoLibre (Debe ser el administrador de la cuenta, no sirve con cuentas de operador).</p>
        </div>
        
        <form action="/signup" method="POST" class="space-y-5">
            <!-- Token de Seguridad Obligatorio en Rails -->
            <%= hidden_field_tag :authenticity_token, form_authenticity_token %>

            <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 mb-1">Nombre y Apellido</label>
                <input type="text" name="user_name" placeholder="Ej: Juan Pérez" required 
                    class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:outline-none transition">
            </div>

            <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 mb-1">Correo Electrónico</label>
                <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="nombre@empresa.com" required 
                    class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:outline-none transition">
            </div>

            <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 mb-1">Crear Contraseña</label>
                <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Mínimo 6 caracteres" required 
                    class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:outline-none transition">
            </div>

            <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 mb-1">Nombre de la Empresa</label>
                <input type="text" name="account_name" placeholder="Ej: Mi Tienda Online" required 
                    class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:outline-none transition">
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-orange-600 text-white py-4 rounded-2xl font-black text-lg hover:bg-orange-700 transition shadow-lg shadow-orange-100">
                Crear cuenta y conectar MercadoLibre
            </button>
        </form>

        <p class="mt-8 text-center text-sm text-gray-400">
            ¿Ya tienes cuenta? <a href="/app/login" class="text-orange-600 font-bold">Inicia sesión aquí</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>